OL,4,Chome of pensioner, 76, before stealing
OL,5,Ccash
OL,7,FThe pensioner was pushed against the
OL,8,Fwall of his hallway, before being
OL,9,Fpushed into his living room where he
OL,10,Ffell to the floor and hit his head.
OL,11,FHis 96-year-old mother was also in the
OL,12,Fhouse at the same time.
OL,14,FIt happened around 4:30pm on Monday 12
OL,15,FFebruary, leaving the victim with a
OL,16,Flump to his head and an injured finger.
OL,18,FThe victim's wallet was stolen before
OL,19,Fa man is seen running out of the
OL,20,Fproperty.
