OL,3,CCCTV shows masked man barging into
OL,4,Chome of pensioner, 76, before stealing
OL,5,Ccash
OL,7,FHe was seen running down an alleyway
OL,8,Ffrom Vincent Gardens onto Randal
OL,9,FStreet, across Craven Road and then
OL,10,Fonto Birkin Avenue before he headed
OL,11,Fdown a path.
OL,13,FDetectives are analysing CCTV,
OL,14,Fdashcam, and doorbell camera footage
OL,15,Fin the area and carrying out forensic
OL,16,Finquiries.
OL,18,FReassurance patrols have also been
OL,19,Fstepped up in the area as detectives
OL,20,Fprogress with their investigation.
