OL,4,Chome of pensioner, 76, before stealing
OL,5,Ccash
OL,7,FThe suspect is described as being
OL,8,Fwhite, of tall and slim build, wearing
OL,9,Fa black hooded top, baseball cap,
OL,10,Fdistinctive khaki-coloured trousers,
OL,11,Fand trainers.
OL,13,FDetective Inspector Chris Berryman, of
OL,14,FNottinghamshire Police, said: "This
OL,15,Fkind of offence is thankfully very
OL,16,Frare, but we are treating this
OL,17,Fincident extremely seriously and we
OL,18,Fare working hard to track down the man
OL,19,Fresponsible.
