OL,7,F"We are calling on the public to help
OL,8,Fus find this violent offender. We
OL,9,Fdon't want this to happen to anyone
OL,10,Felse.
OL,12,F"This was a particularly nasty attack
OL,13,Fon a vulnerable victim in his own home
OL,14,Fwhich left him with injuries. His 96-
OL,15,Fyear-old mother was also in the
OL,16,Fproperty at the time.
OL,18,F"Think how you'd feel if this was your
OL,19,Fmother, father, grandmother,
OL,20,Fgrandfather or member of your family
OL,21,Fwho had been targeted in this way."
